<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Jenny K Walsh,Links</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Funnel+Display:wght@300..800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;1,400;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      background: #fff;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
      padding: 32px;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── HEADER ── */
    .header {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 18vw, 7rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .header h1 span {
      display: block;
      color: #F6FF00;
      -webkit-text-stroke: 2px #1a1a1a;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 400px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    /* ── PORTFOLIO ── */
    .block-portfolio {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      transform: rotate(-1deg);
    }

    .block-portfolio .eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      opacity: 0.5;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .block-portfolio a {
      display: block;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 9vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      color: #F6FF00;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .block-portfolio a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── YOUTUBE ── */
    .block-youtube {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      border: 3px solid #1a1a1a;
      transform: rotate(0.5deg);
    }

    .block-youtube .eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      opacity: 0.4;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .block-youtube a {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 7vw, 2.5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .block-youtube a:hover { color: #FF00FF; }

    .block-youtube .sub {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-top: 0.4rem;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    /* ── PHOTOGRAPHY ── */
    .block-photo {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      padding: 1.25rem 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }

    .block-photo p {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .block-photo a {
      font-family: 'Funnel Display', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 6vw, 2rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: #F6FF00;
      padding: 0 4px;
    }

    .block-photo a:hover { background: #00FFFF; }

    /* ── CATS ── */
    .block-cats {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: #F6FF00;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      transform: rotate(-0.5deg);
    }

    .block-cats .intro-text {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .cats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .cat a {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .cat-name {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 8vw, 2.5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .cat-sub {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .cat a:hover .cat-name { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── POTTERY ── */
    .block-pottery {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .block-pottery .label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      opacity: 0.45;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .pottery-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .pottery-links a {
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 5vw, 1.75rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #F6FF00;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .pottery-links a:hover { color: #F6FF00; }

    /* ── SOCIALS ── */
    .block-socials {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }

    .block-socials p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .social-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .social-links a {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #00FFFF;
    }

    .social-links a:hover { border-color: #FF00FF; }

    /* ── GEOCITIES ── */
    .block-geocities {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.6;
      opacity: 0.35;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* ── BYE ── */
    .bye {
      font-size: clamp(5rem, 25vw, 10rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 0.9;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      transform: rotate(2deg);
      display: inline-block;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .bye span {
      color: #FF00FF;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <h1>Oh, hi<span>there!</span></h1>
    <div class="intro">
      <p>You're looking for some sort of link,let's see if I can help you.</p>
      <p>I exist in far too many places across the web, an inevitable artifact of being online since the mid-90s. Can't do much about it, so here are a few places you'll find me.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="block-portfolio">
    <p class="eyebrow">Product design</p>
    <a href="https://jennykwalsh.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">jennykwalsh.com →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="block-youtube">
    <p class="eyebrow">Video</p>
    <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube →</a>
    <p class="sub">acrobatics · circus · yurts · #1SecondEveryday</p>
  </div>

  <div class="block-photo">
    <p>If you'd like to see more of my photography, I have a client gallery that captures a small portion of it.</p>
    <a href="https://formpixelphotography.pic-time.com/client" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Form &amp; Pixel Photography →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="block-cats">
    <p class="intro-text">I've also got instas for Roland and Pixel, which they rarely update but still get more engagement than I do (deservedly so).</p>
    <div class="cats-grid">
      <div class="cat">
        <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <div class="cat-name">Roland</div>
          <div class="cat-sub">Instagram →</div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="cat">
        <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <div class="cat-name">Pixel</div>
          <div class="cat-sub">Instagram →</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="block-pottery">
    <p class="label">The pottery situation</p>
    <div class="pottery-links">
      <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shop</a>
      <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="block-socials">
    <p>Other socials, if you're into that kinda thing.</p>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="https://www.threads.net/@lemonjenny" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Threads</a>
      <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pinterest</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="block-geocities">There's more, dating back to Geocities and OG Blogger and all manner of old websites I've built... but we're gonna let those die in the archives.</p>

  <div>
    <span class="bye">Bye<span>!</span></span>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
